        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Communities Helping Invest through Property and Improvements Needed for Veterans Act or the CHIP IN for Veterans Act</strong></p> <p>This bill extends from 5 to 10 years the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) pilot program under which the VA may accept donations of property or facilities from specified entities (e.g., state or local authorities).<br> </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
